rows.label: qev092805_MSG0010
rows.name: So it's come to this, has it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0015
rows.name: You disappoint me once again, Alicia dear.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0020
rows.name: Boss, I...![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0030
rows.name: You are a part of this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0040
rows.name:
I thought you'd at least have the sense 
to realize you were being watched.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0050
rows.name:
Then you admit it?
All the heinous crimes you've committed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0060
rows.name:
What does it matter if you denounce me now?
It doesn't change a thing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0070
rows.name: Learn when to back off, Liesel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0080
rows.name: Not a chance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0090
rows.name:
Oh, it's one rule for your friends,
and another for the rest of us, is it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0100
rows.name: No. You both need to atone for what you've done.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0110
rows.name: How savage. So you would forsake her?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0120
rows.name:
Anyone who asks for forgivenessâ€”
I'll gladly reach out a hand to them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0130
rows.name:
But you? Do you even have remorse?
Do you even care?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0140
rows.name:
I see. Liesel...you really are
upright to a fault, aren't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0150
rows.name: ...Sickening.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0160
rows.name: Better than killing people just to make a quick buck.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_JNK0170
rows.name: Show Resolve

rows.label: qev092805_SEL0180
rows.name: Say there's only one way out of this.

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0190
rows.name: I agree.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0195
rows.name: This guy isn't just a villain... He's scum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_JNK0200
rows.name: Act Cocky

rows.label: qev092805_SEL0210
rows.name: Say she can put this one on your tab.

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0220
rows.name: It's true. I've lost count of how many I owe you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0230
rows.name: Though...you're worth every cent![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0240
rows.name: Negotiations have broken down, then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0250
rows.name:
"She set out on an unauthorized expedition
and perished in the wilderness."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0255
rows.name:
I'll write something to that effect
in my final report.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0260
rows.name: It's over, Kelemen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092805_MSG0265
rows.name: Time to pay the piper.[ST:wait ]
